{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"http://ghost.local:8000","title":"Ghost Docs","description":"Everything you need to know about working with the Ghost professional publishing platform."}},"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"plural","date":"2018-10-01","date_pretty":"01 October, 2018","path":null,"meta_title":"Ghost Handlebars Theme Helpers: plural","meta_description":"Output how many posts exist in a collection in your Ghost publication using the plural handlebars helper. Read more about Ghost themes! ðŸ‘»","image":null,"next":null,"sidebar":"handlebars","toc":null,"keywords":["api","handlebars","themes","helpers"]},"html":"<p>Usage: <code class=\"language-text\">{{plural value empty=&quot;&quot; singular=&quot;&quot; plural=&quot;&quot;}}</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"description\"><a href=\"#description\" aria-label=\"description permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Description</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">{{plural}}</code> is a formatting helper for outputting strings which change depending on whether a number is singular or plural.</p>\n<p>The most common use case for the plural helper is outputting information about how many posts there are in total in a collection. For example, themes have access to <code class=\"language-text\">pagination.total</code> on the homepage, a tag page or an author page. You can override the default text.</p>\n<h3 id=\"examples\"><a href=\"#examples\" aria-label=\"examples permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Examples</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"handlebars\"><pre class=\"language-handlebars\"><code class=\"language-handlebars\"><span class=\"token handlebars language-handlebars\"><span class=\"token delimiter punctuation\">{{</span><span class=\"token variable\">plural</span> <span class=\"token variable\">pagination</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token variable\">total</span> <span class=\"token variable\">empty</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'No posts'</span> <span class=\"token variable\">singular</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'% post'</span> <span class=\"token variable\">plural</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'% posts'</span><span class=\"token delimiter punctuation\">}}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">%</code> is parsed by Ghost and will be replaced by the number of posts. This is a specific behaviour for the helper.</p>","fields":{"slug":"/api/handlebars-themes/helpers/plural/"},"timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"Usage: Description is a formatting helper for outputting strings which change depending on whether a number is singular or plural.The mostâ€¦","fileAbsolutePath":"/Users/zhangh/opt/classes/website1/computervisionsite/content/api/v2/handlebars-themes/helpers/plural.md"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/api/handlebars-themes/helpers/plural/"}}